snippet.title: Amber Heard and Elon Musk have not rekindled their romance
snippet.description:
'They are definitely not back together': Exes Amber Heard and Elon Musk have not rekindled their romance... despite intimate lunch together.
They were spotted enjoying a cozy breakfast date together on Thursday.

But despite the intimate outing, Amber Heard and Elon Musk are not back together.

The 31-year-old actress and 46-year-old Tesla founder have not rekindled their romance according to a Friday report from People.
